  "concepts": [
    {
      "title": "Cosine Rule",
      "conceptBody": "<h3><strong>Cosine rule&nbsp;</strong></h3><p>In any triangle $\\text{ABC}$ we have</p><p>$\\begin{array}{*{35}{r}} {{a}^{2}}={{b}^{2}}+{{c}^{2}}-2bc\\text{cos}A \\\\ {{b}^{2}}={{c}^{2}}+{{a}^{2}}-2ca\\text{cos}B \\\\ {{c}^{2}}={{a}^{2}}+{{b}^{2}}-2ab\\text{cos}C \\\\ \\text{cos}A=\\frac{{{b}^{2}}+{{c}^{2}}-{{a}^{2}}}{2bc} \\\\ \\text{cos}B=\\frac{{{a}^{2}}+{{c}^{2}}-{{b}^{2}}}{2ac} \\\\ \\text{cos}C=\\frac{{{a}^{2}}+{{b}^{2}}-{{c}^{2}}}{2ab} \\\\ \\end{array}$</p>",
      "position": 0,
      "qcConcept": "66a0ddabc03b9dcaf1afec30"
    },
    {
      "title": "Projection Formula",
      "conceptBody": "<h3><strong>Projection formula</strong></h3><p>$\\begin{array}{*{35}{r}} {} &amp; a=b\\text{cos}C+c\\text{cos}B \\\\ {} &amp; b=c\\text{cos}A+a\\text{cos}C \\\\ {} &amp; c=a\\text{cos}B+b\\text{cos}A \\\\ \\end{array}$</p>",
      "position": 1,
      "qcConcept": "66a0ddacc03b9dcaf1afec31"
    }
  ],
